title: doc: small typo in doc/faq site
body:
by **atkaaz**: 
on this page: http://golang.org/doc/faq#language_changes

the phrase:
Even if your proposal is compatible with the Go 1 spec, it may be not be in the spirit
of Go's design goals.

this part:
it may be not be

should be:
it may not be

or at the very worst:
it maybe not be
